      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i need some advice. my neighbor just changed their wifi name to \"WE SEE YOU IN THE KITCHEN\" and honestly i'm getting really creeped out. like the signal strength literally fluctuates whenever i walk into that room. do u think they're using some kind of tracking software or something?",
